Package com.project.moviebooking.repository

package com.project.moviebooking.repository
The "repository" package contains repository interfaces and classes responsible for interacting with data storage and performing CRUD operations within the movie booking application.

Repository interfaces and implementations in this package define contracts for accessing and managing persistent data entities. These repositories often utilize underlying frameworks or libraries to communicate with the database or data storage layer, providing data access functionality to other parts of the application.

Organizing repositories in this package helps maintain a clear separation of concerns, promoting modular and testable data access operations within the movie booking system.
